---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NewsletterForm from '../components/NewsletterForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About | Mohammed Rahman"
  description="Learn about Mohammed Rahman's background, story, and journey."
  currentPage="about"
>
  <div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-heading font-bold uppercase mb-12">
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-16">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold uppercase mb-6">
          My Story
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I am a Mechanical Engineering graduate with a strong interest in how ideas move from concept to real, usable designs. My journey into engineering grew from a curiosity about how things work and developed through academic study, hands-on design projects, and practical problem-solving. During my degree, I became particularly drawn to design-focused engineering, where technical thinking meets creativity and real-world constraints.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Alongside my studies, I actively developed practical skills through CAD modelling, independent projects, and experimenting with modern digital tools. I enjoy learning by building, testing, and refining ideas, and this mindset shapes how I approach challengesâ€”breaking them down logically and improving them through iteration. This website documents that journey and shows how my skills and interests continue to evolve.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold uppercase mb-6">
          Background
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          My background is in Mechanical Engineering, with experience in engineering design, technical drawing, and BIM workflows. I have completed projects using AutoCAD and Revit, developing skills in creating accurate drawings, structured models, and clear design documentation.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
          Through academic and personal projects, I have built experience in engineering design processes, CAD modelling, problem-solving, and presenting technical work clearly. I am particularly interested in how traditional engineering skills can be strengthened through efficient workflows, digital tools, and AI-assisted development.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold uppercase mb-6">
          Current Focus
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I am currently focused on developing my design capability and exploring modern "vibe coding" workflows that combine engineering thinking with AI tools. I am building projects in CAD, BIM, and web-based portfolios to showcase my work and learning process.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
          This site will continue to grow as I add new projects, document what I am learning, and experiment at the intersection of engineering, design, and technology. Click below to explore my projects and see what I am currently working on.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Newsletter Signup Section -->
    <section class="border-t-2 border-green-dark pt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold uppercase mb-6 text-center">
        Stay Connected
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-white/90 text-center mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Newsletter description -->
        Join my weekly newsletter to receive updates, insights, and exclusive content.
      </p>
      <NewsletterForm variant="secondary" />
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

